718080f-a.text:
Cannon Street, north from and including Broome Street. Also shon aoross the vacant lot at the S.W. corner, is Nos. 68-70 and a portion of No. 72 Broome Street, at adjoining and west of the N.W. corner of Cannon
Street.
February 12, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.

717850f-a.text:
Broome Street. west from Cannon Street. Note the park in the right center (just beyond the soiitary No. 82 Broome) where the north R. Hoe and Co. plant formerly stood. Barely discernible on the left is the modern apartment house facing on same.
NEG~ 3E57  May 7, 1939
P. L. Sperr
